{"tid":1527090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅頭文件証武警入港","createTime":"2019-09-01T08:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:37:08.000Z","uid":296751,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3025bb4684e88e5e8a457599692580ce27c81b","tid":1527090,"uid":296751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"武警入港不是空穴來風，有人爆出紅頭文件<br />\n題目寫明武警已做好來香港維穩的準備&hellip;&hellip;分分鍾拉返大陸<br />\n聽日大家出街一定要小心<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hgMNai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hgMNai.jpg&h=17837ae2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38289078973ae720cde6c0fb533f9a4fa20f7a9b","tid":1527090,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60888ef0dce5452d31c805bceee7c02613b6633f","tid":1527090,"uid":156326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"影成咁做乜鳩"},{"pid":"4e07d87ab8d963ea8176dd5a2ec78db4c6b36fbc","tid":1527090,"uid":85557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"衰撚過打格仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7388fe3afec92ae5f5280ad28ced33337667b390","tid":1527090,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:56:17.000Z","msg":"已滲入"},{"pid":"fbbfe2af7a738d103920e117f333e3d894fc54dd","tid":1527090,"uid":72800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:56:30.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n外國戰線<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人道災難<br />\n純洩憤 衝入車廂無調查 無拘捕 齋打人</span></strong></span><br />\n情緒失控 行為失控<br />\n妄顧公眾安全 人身權利<br />\n濫暴 濫用私刑 酷刑凌辱<br />\n<br />\n阻礙救援 違反國際人道法<br />\n封鎖現場多個小時 隔離救護員進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港正受人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n公然妨礙新聞自由 警方出公關稿籲媒體跟從<br />\n截斷交通 封鎖去道<br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span></span><br />\n實彈已出 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<br />\n召喚攬炒巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefaf9f930aebcddb2afa2650810a883d00610ad","tid":1527090,"uid":94666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:00:11.000Z","msg":"又嚇鬼，機密文件會流出？真係要做洗撚話你知？"},{"pid":"4fa7e21f48d680dc430f6cbee347720f51d1625c","tid":1527090,"uid":248384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:06:12.000Z","msg":"逐個逐個字係到估"},{"pid":"b603c1c8d04cac7a7677fe49d545b85ec3811e08","tid":1527090,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c1131d52fdc0fba9eac3d99989ce47c468e9efb","tid":1527090,"uid":268250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"你又係p牌 我又係p牌<br />\n點解你會有機密資料仲要濛成咁"},{"pid":"b2a59c4a91fb29d8c9b04d4c0e805ea75fb59619","tid":1527090,"uid":22707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c1131d52fdc0fba9eac3d99989ce47c468e9efb","tid":1527090,"uid":268250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"你又係p牌 我又係p牌<br />\n點解你會有機密資料仲要濛成咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:14:53.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78146af0adfde4e19a3933b6ab3414feeecd800","tid":1527090,"uid":41458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":